dc_title_s: Sea floor topography and backscatter intensity of the Hudson canyon region offshore of New York and New Jersey
dc_description_s: These maps show the sea floor topography and backscatter intensity of the Hudson Canyon region on the continental slope and rise offshore of New Jersey and New York. Sheet 1 shows sea floor topography as shaded relief. Sheet 2 shows sea floor topography as shaded relief with backscatter intensity superimposed in color.
